   <body>
      <div>
         <p>As an option, if battery temperature compensation or measurement
is needed a battery temperature sensor can be selected.</p>
         <p>The
battery temperature sensor connection is located on the monitoring
controller.</p>
         <note>After the batteries are installed the position
of the temperature sensor should be checked. It is recommended to
place the temperature sensor close to a battery cell in the middle
of the battery bank.</note>
